   <category name='food'>

      <section name='reception'>

         <para number='1' comment='Buy food - reception - 530'>
         You put ten groats into one of the machines, and a foil container drops out into your hands. You wait while it heats up, then when it reaches the desired temperature, you remove the lid, revealing the meat pie contained within. It's not at all bad, for vending machine food - the pastry isn't too stale, the meat seems to have come from a real live animal, and the gravy is reasonably tasty and only a little bit glutinous.
         </para>

         <para number='2'>
         You finish the pie and drop the empty foil dish into the receptacle next to the machine, where it will be recycled.
         </para>

         <para number='3' comment='No money'>
         You look through all the pockets in your nano-chameleon suit but cannot find enough money.
         </para>

      </section>

   </category>

   <category name='moves'>

      <section name='noexit'>

         <para number='1' comment='Shuttle port - loc 402'>
         For security reasons you are not allowed to wander around on the surface of the asteroid.
         </para>

         <para number='2' comment='Security - loc 531'>
         Your attempt to move in a direction which is not the exit sparks a major security alert.
         </para>

      </section>

